_sText:
Map by THEnub aka thenub641 

Custom textures and sounds by myself, be sure to ask me on GBB or find me on steam if you want to use or 
re-release this map or any part of it.

Notes: 
--I know there's issues with the radar, can't be helped, I could never quite get it figured out. Anyone
who happens to make a functional one is more than welcome to let me know and either re-release it or simply let
me update the current release.
--I had originally optimized a nav file for bot use as well, but it was lost due to hard drive failure and I'm
not looking to spend the time doing it all again. Again, anyone willing to do it themselves is permitted to
re-release or send the file to me to update (but you must contact me first, regardless).

THEnub 05/27/2012


NAV FILE UPDATE BELOW
------------------
Hey all! Thanks to Meurglis3, there is now an optimized .nav file for this map. Once again, at last! You can go ahead and download it from [here](http://css.gamebanana.com/gamefiles/3372 "Go to the Gamebanana Submission")! 

Thanks again Meurglis3! 

THEnub 1/22/2014
